    "description": "Join the Tata Communications family as a Senior Software Engineer in Kanpur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Tata Communications:\nTata Communications is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata Communications!",
